data.name: grdDOC4003.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.SYS_DATE , A.SYS_ID , A.UPD_DATE , A.UPD_ID , A.HOSP_CODE , A.PKDOC4003 , A.SEQ , TO_DATE(A.CREATE_DATE, 'YY/MM/DD') CREATE_DATE , A.TO_HOSPITAL_INFO , A.TO_SINRYOUKA , A.TO_SINRYOUKA2 , A.TO_DOCTOR , A.TO_DOCTOR2 , A.DOCTOR , A.GWA , A.SUNAME , A.SEX , A.ZIP , A.ADDRESS , A.TEL , TO_DATE(A.BIRTH, 'YY/MM/DD') BIRTH , A.JOB , A.DISEASE , A.CHECKUP_OPINION , A.PRESCRIPTION , A.BUNHO , SUBSTR(B.ZIP_CODE, 1, 3) || '-' || SUBSTR(B.ZIP_CODE, 4) ZIP_CODE , B.ADDRESS , 'TEL:' || B.TEL || ' FAX:' || B.FAX , B.YOYANG_NAME FROM DOC4003 A , BAS0001 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho -- AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.CREATE_DATE BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND B.END_DATE ORDER BY A.SEQ DESC
